<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="seriously-adv">seriously <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'sɪəriəsli/    美 /'sɪriəsli/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>严重地；认真地：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>seriously ill / injured</strong>
病得/伤得严重</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="take-sb-sth-seriously">take sb / sth seriously</h3>
<p>1.<strong>认真对待某人 / 某事：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Let’s see the difficulties as a kind of test and take them seriously.
让我们把困难看做一种考验，认真地对待吧！</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>He began to take political science <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (serious) only when he left school.  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. seriously  </p></div>